Post-Match Reflections: Marko Arnautovic: 'The last two games are exactly us'
Ralf Rangnick: 'We were a bit lucky at the start when Haaland hit the post, but even then we controlled the game'
Christoph Baumgartner: 'I'm convinced that we can also win both games in November'
Miscellaneous Highlights: Austria are now tied on seven points with leaders Norway and Slovenia
Others: Austria are schedule to visit Kazakhstan and host Slovenia next month
